@echo off COLOR 08 title SERVERNAME HERE Client "C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe" -cp . *.java "C:\Program Files\Java\jdr1.5.0_00\bin\java.exe" server pause

And if that doesnt work you need to update your java…
